            <h3 id="section-1-4">1.4 Cost by Major Metro Market</h3>

            <p>A Bedder World's analysis of removal costs across 800+ US markets shows an average of $135, with significant regional variation driven by labor costs, landfill tipping fees, and local recycling regulations.</p>

            <p><strong>Most Expensive Markets:</strong></p>
