                <li>COVID-related service disruptions (2020-2021)</li>
                <li>Rapid inflation across labor and fuel costs (2021-2023)</li>
                <li>Increased landfill tipping fees nationwide</li>
                <li>Rising demand as consumers upgraded home furnishings during the pandemic</li>
            </ul>

            <p>This 4% annual increase aligns with broader service industry trends and is expected to continue as landfill fees rise and more states consider recycling mandates.</p>
